data.text:
Important phone numbers

Phone support is available in 100+ different languages

Call 8-1-1 to connect with a registered nurse for free, secure and confidential health advice, 24/7

Call 2-1-1 to find social services, financial assistance programs, or community supports, 24/7

416-217-2077 Toronto Seniors Helpline: 9am - 8pm weekdays, 10am - 6pm weekends and stat holidays
